LVGL:
make BOARD=csim now requires lv_port_linux support.  See notes in 
lvglConfigPanel project for setting up and configuring lv_port_linux

arduino versions:
makeEspArduino requires arduino-cli core install esp32:esp32@3.2.0

libraries:
csim needs TinyGPSPlus version 1.1.0, not available in arduino-cli lib upgrade
